<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Fire is rare in moist alpine and subalpine meadows where the alliance occurs. Flooding adjacent to streams and freeze-thaw, avalanches, gopher disturbance, and bioturbation rather than fire regularly impact stands of this alliance.</div>
